# 4. Runtime Architecture Constraints

The chatbot must operate completely **offline inside the browser**.

Users will access the chatbot by opening:

file://index.html

This means the runtime system must not depend on:

* backend servers
* databases
* web services
* third-party APIs
* external AI services

All retrieval and search logic must run directly in **JavaScript inside the browser environment**.

